Chinese Farmer 's Wife Gives Birth To Quadruplets
CHONGQING , November 22 ( Xinhua ) -- The wife of a farmer in Chongqing municipality has given birth to a male and three female babies .
According to a the hospital in the Xiufeng District where they were born , the four babies are doing well .
They weighed between 1,500 and 2,000 grams when they were born on September 29 .
When the woman had a check-up in August because her abdomen was abnormally large , the county hospital did an ultrasound test and decided that she should have a Caesarean section at the Xiufeng District hospital .
